# Usage
	quack <file>

# Description
	Fuchas quack is a tool to edit files with basic optional syntax highlighting.

	The quack command has only one operation mode which opens <file> and open a visual editor.

# Options
	--file-language=<lang>
		Set the syntax highlighting language to <lang>.

	-n, --no-syntax-highlighting
		Disable syntax highlighting and use the default color for all of the text.
